function EventSystem:CountActiveListeners()
    local count = 0
    for eventType, listeners in pairs(self.listeners) do
        for _, listener in ipairs(listeners) do
            if listener.isActive then
                count = count + 1
            end
        end
    end
    return count
end
function_129.name: CountActiveListeners

function GameSession:UpdateScore(points)
    self.score = self.score + points
    print(string.format("⭐ 会话 %s 得分更新: +%d (总分: %d)", self.id, points, self.score))
    return self.score
end
function_207.name: UpdateScore

function_328.functionBody:
function User:AddExperience(amount)
    self.experience = self.experience + amount
    local newLevel = math.floor(self.experience / 100) + 1
    if newLevel > self.level then
        self.level = newLevel
        print(string.format("🎉 用户 %s 升级到 %d 级!", self.name, self.level))
    end
end
function_328.name: AddExperience
